; Issue: https://github.com/rustledger/rustledger/issues/364
; Description: Formatter strips comments, metadata, and whitespace
; Expected: All comments, metadata, and blank lines should be preserved
;
; This file tests that the formatter preserves:
; 1. Standalone comments (like this one)
; 2. Metadata on directives
; 3. Blank lines between sections

option "title" "Issue 364 Test"
option "operating_currency" "USD"

; === Account Setup ===

2024-01-01 open Assets:Bank:Checking USD
  description: "Primary checking account"
  bank: "First National"

2024-01-01 open Expenses:Food USD

; === Transactions ===

2024-01-15 * "Coffee Shop" "Morning coffee"
  memo: "With colleagues"
  Expenses:Food  5.00 USD
  Assets:Bank:Checking

; End of file comment
